# Implement Zing MP3 Downloader

## Goal
Add a new tool to download high-quality music from Zing MP3, accessible within the "Tool" section of the web app.

## Architecture
Reusing the successful pattern from Instagram Downloader:
`Frontend Component` -> `Cloudflare Function` -> `n8n Webhook` -> `External API (api.satoru.click)`

## Components

### 1. n8n Workflow (`Zing MP3 Download API.json`)
- **Trigger**: Webhook POST `/zing-download`
- **Action**: HTTP Request GET `https://api.satoru.click/api/zingmp3?link={link}`
- **Response**: JSON data from Satoru API.

### 2. Cloudflare Function (`functions/api/zingmp3.ts`)
- Proxy endpoint that forwards requests from Frontend to n8n.
- Securely manages the n8n webhook URL via environment variables.

### 3. Frontend Component (`src/components/ZingMp3Download.tsx`)
- UI Input for Zing MP3 URL.
- Display Result:
    - Song Title & Artist
    - Thumbnail (Square)
    - Audio Player (Preview)
    - Download Button (Force Download)

### 4. App Integration ([src/App.tsx](file:///i:/Workflow/n8n/Workflow/Backups/web-fontend-v2/src/App.tsx))
- Refactor `NavItem.TOOL` view.
- Introduce a "Tool Switcher" (Tabs) to toggle between:
    - Instagram Downloader
    - Zing MP3 Downloader

